  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy women 65 or older with a family history of memory problems not currently on
             estrogen.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Significant neurological impairment

          -  Current estrogen use

          -  History of breast cancer
      </textblock>
